2. PDF.js / pdfjs-dist (PDF rendering in the browser)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Component name:   PDF.js (Mozilla pdf.js / npm pdfjs-dist)
  Copyright:        Copyright 2022 Mozilla Foundation (see @licstart block in each bundled file)
  Project / source: https://github.com/mozilla/pdf.js
  License:          Apache License, Version 2.0

  Files included in this plugin:
    - mod/pdfannotator/lib/pdfjs/pdf.min.js
    - mod/pdfannotator/lib/pdfjs/pdf.worker.min.js

  Full license text (verbatim copy of Apache-2.0):
    mod/pdfannotator/lib/pdfjs/LICENSE-APACHE-2.0.txt

  Short attribution / pointers:
    mod/pdfannotator/lib/pdfjs/PDFJS-ATTRIBUTION.txt

  Purpose:
    In-browser PDF parsing and rendering for the PDF Annotator activity;
    the scripts are registered in locallib.php.

  Embedded notice:
    The minified bundles include the Mozilla @licstart / @licend Apache-2.0
    header comment at the top of each file.


